rComments: The words "**** you, Will Baker" frequently came out my my mouth during the semester that I took this course.  I was an A student in AP English for 2 years in high school and I ended up getting at B+ in this class.  And the class is about basketball....honestly.....get out while you still can.

I hate Will Baker and you will too. For a required class he grades way too hard and has an obsession with sports. Every paper written was about basketball, and even those who loved sports hated the class. Switch out of his section!
I SECOND THAT!!! WORST TEACHER EVER!! AND WORST PERSON EVER!!!GET OUT WHILE U CAN!
Honestly- this guy sucks. Worst teacher ever, terrible humor, and complete jerk. if you have him- switch out!
He is a funny guy, very cynical at times, but still a good teacher. He is a very hard grader. He wants you to make a very specific argument in each paper.

This guy is really funny, but he is a really hard grader. You'll hear about other Rhet classes and how they do nothing. This guy makes you work pretty hard for your grade. If you want an easy rhet class, don't take him. Although, he's pretty funny.
